'''DirectX Video Acceleration'''（'''DXVA'''）是在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台的Microsoft API规范，能让[[视频编解码器|视频解码器]]使用硬件解码（俗稱'''硬解'''）。

DXVA 1.0最早是在[[Windows_2000|Windows 2000]]以及[[Windows_98|Windows 98]]版本開始引入的API，可以使用於[[DirectShow|VMR 7/9]]之上。<ref name="dxva2">{{cite web | title = DirectX Video Acceleration 2.0 | url = http://msdn2.microsoft.com/en-us/library/aa965263.aspx | accessdate = 2007-10-24 | archive-date = 2012-04-23 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/678aLE0lb?url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/aa965263.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref> DXVA 2.0僅適用於[[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]、[[Windows_7|Windows 7]]以及更新的版本，被整合於[[Media_Foundation|Media Foundation]]（MF）並使用[[Media_Foundation#增強型視訊渲染器|EVR]]。<ref name="dxva2"/>

==功能==
显卡芯片在硬件上支援DXVA规范，并不代表它就实现了DXVA所有功能。DXVA制定硬件加速解码可分四级：
*VLD：控制BitStream
*IDCT（反餘弦變換）：IDCT级别的解码包含MoComp和PostProc
*MoComp，运动补偿，Pixel Prediction
*PostProc
其中以VLD加速等级最高，老舊的显卡如Geforce3只支持MC加速，GeForce 8000和Radeon HD 2000都可以支援VLD。[[PowerDVD|PowerDVD]]分别可以对H.264、VC-1、MPEG2、X264、XVID、DVIX等格式进行解压。此外DXVA還定義了一組可以讓圖形驅動實現運算加速的硬件驅動接口（Device Driver Interfaces/DDIs）。

DXVA定義了運動補償DDI，屬於[[Inverse_discrete_cosine_transform|iDCT]]動作介面，[[霍夫曼编码|霍夫曼编码]]，[[運動補償|運動補償]]、[[alpha_blending|alpha blending]]、inverse {{link-en|quantization|Quantization (image processing)}}、[[色彩管理|color space conversion]]以及幀率的變化動作，還有其他。<ref name="intro">{{cite web | url = http://msdn2.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms799545.aspx | title = Introduction to DirectX VA | accessdate = 2007-10-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/678aLnI2l?url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms799545.aspx | archivedate = 2012-04-23 | df =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://forum.videolan.org/viewtopic.php?t=9421 | title = Microsoft DirectX Video Acceleration (DirectX VA) support | accessdate = 2007-10-24 | archive-date = 2012-04-23 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/678aMSjF5?url=http://forum.videolan.org/viewtopic.php?t=9421 | dead-url = no }}</ref>其本身又有三個小細項：Deinterlacing DDI, COPP DDI以及ProcAmp DDI.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://msdn2.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms798379.aspx | title = DirectX Video Acceleration | accessdate = 2007-10-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/678exRdk0?url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms798379.aspx | archivedate = 2012-04-23 | df =  }}</ref>[[deinterlace|Deinterlacing]] DDI定義了針對[[deinterlace|deinterlacing]]動作的回饋. COPP（Certified Output Protection Protocol）DDI可允許管道（pipeline）在[[数字版权管理|DRM-protected media]]安全性考量，定義加密功能. ProcAmp DDI用於加速[[post-processing|post-processing]] video.<!-- The ProcAmp driver module sits between the hardware video renderer and the display driver and provides functions for applying post-processing filters on the decompressed video.-->

